  "description": "Herbalism is the study and practice of using plants and plant extracts for therapeutic purposes. It spans multiple traditions — Western herbalism, [Traditional Chinese Medicine](../traditional-chinese-medicine/_index.md), Ayurveda, Indigenous plant medicine practices worldwide — and interfaces with modern [pharmacology](../pharmacology/_index.md) through pharmacognosy (the study of drugs derived from natural sources).",
